                        </div>
                        <div class="formula-note">
                            <strong>Upper bound:</strong> Assumes entire chromosomes inherited as blocks<br>
                            <strong>Biological meaning:</strong> Maximum possible Mendelian sampling variance<br>
                            <strong>s<sub>m</sub>, d<sub>m</sub>:</strong> Sire and dam haplotypes; <strong>a<sub>m</sub>:</strong> marker effects
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="formula-box">
                        <div class="formula-title">üìà Mendelian Sampling Variance (No Linkage)</div>
