                    </div>
                    <div class="formula-main">
                        SL<sub>U</sub> = Œ£<sub>m=1</sub><sup>43,382</sup> max<sub>L</sub> (l<sub>m</sub>a<sub>m</sub>)
                    </div>
                    <div class="formula-note">
                        <strong>SL<sub>C</sub>:</strong> Realistic limit using best chromosome haplotypes<br>
                        <strong>SL<sub>U</sub>:</strong> Theoretical maximum using best allele at each locus<br>
                        <strong>H:</strong> Haplotype population; <strong>L:</strong> All observed alleles
