                                    <strong>MSU calculation:</strong> Sum individual marker effects (no linkage assumption)<br>
                                    <strong>Validation:</strong> Expected MS = ¬Ω additive genetic variance falls between bounds<br>
                                    <strong>Biological verification:</strong> MSC > MSU as expected from linkage theory
                                </div>
                                <p><strong>Elegant solution:</strong> By calculating both extremes, they provided bounds that must contain the true biological value, regardless of the actual linkage patterns.</p>
